%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/Th%C3%B4n-x%C3%A1-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-4bMFrUtSf1-0Y24g9fq1Vw">Thôn xá kỳ 1 - 村舍其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Y%C3%AAn-thu%E1%BB%B7-t%E1%BA%A7m-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-9r7f8VSP4jfBL7RzYvAu0A">Vô đề (Yên thuỷ tầm thường sự) - 無題（煙水尋常事）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/Xu%C3%A2n-v%C5%A9-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-k%C3%BD-T%E1%BA%ADp-M%E1%BB%B9/poem-5D6foYRh8iWc-R_TK5MtTA">Xuân vũ tức sự ký Tập Mỹ - 春雨即事寄襲美</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/author-FCMLXx_iJwv1UkwFEUT-cw">Lục Quy Mông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
